data.description: This beautiful 3bed/2bath home, nestled in a quiet neighborhood in Stuarts Draft; is a perfect place for a family! The 1.08 acre lot offers a great space to enjoy the outdoors, plenty of room for a garden; or other fun activities. The basement also has space to work with..to all of my guys..man cave anybody? With numerous updates made to the home, and an HVAC, plumbing, and roof only being a couple of years old; I believe someone will walk in and have a sense of comfort knowing they could be the new owners of this wonderful home!
